    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a museum-grade 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the highly desirable 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant delivers 385 hp with a linear torque curve, paired to a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle. The vehicle is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and the Sport Chrono Plus package, ensuring precise damping and aggressive throttle mapping. Mechanically, this example is flawless: the undercarriage is pristine, bushings are supple, and the bore-scoring concerns of predecessors are non-existent here. The Basalt Black Metallic paint retains a deep, swirl-free luster with consistent micron readings across all panels. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state, with no delamination of touchpoints and perfect bolster integrity on the adaptive sport seats. Fully documented service history included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
