      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, reflecting a standard of care that satisfies the most discerning collector. Every surface and mechanical component has been meticulously preserved to maintain original factory integrity. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade acquisition.",
