    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade JZA80 chassis featuring the iconic 2JZ-GTE sequential twin-turbocharged inline-six. This example remains in factory-stock configuration, retaining its original twin-scroll turbines with zero shaft play and a pristine side-mount intercooler. Power is managed by the bulletproof Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a Torsen limited-slip differential. The mechanical integrity is absolute, with no vacuum leaks, perfect compression across all cylinders, and crisp gear synchronization. The suspension retains its original double-wishbone geometry with firm bushings and no signs of fluid weep on the dampers. All factory VIN tags are intact, and the undercarriage is immaculate, showing no oxidation or fatigue. This is a rare opportunity for the purist to own a mechanically synchronized masterpiece of 90s performance engineering.",
